shining cuckoo
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a small migratory bird, Chrysococcyx lucidus, with glossy deep-green back (also called bronze(-wing(ed)) cuckoo, pipiwharauroa).
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
